Class EditApptController

java.lang.Object
controller.EditApptController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class EditApptController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
The class controls the user interaction in editAppt.fxml. Appt information is populated into the form. User edits the information for update in database.
